about.projectDescription: Designed to transform the city skyline, Downtown Terraces stands as a pinnacle of contemporary architectural excellence and urban sophistication. This landmark project showcases elegant, glass-fronted towers offering sweeping city vistas, with luxurious residences featuring cutting-edge amenities and smart home technology. Located in the heart of the city, it offers easy access to business districts, cultural attractions, and top dining and entertainment spots.

amenities.text: Every detail has been carefully selected to create a luxurious and comfortable atmosphere. The Downtown Terraces offer exclusive amenities that cater to the refined tastes of their residents and guests. Lavish lounges and common areas provide peaceful retreats for relaxation and socializing, featuring plush seating and panoramic city views. Residential units have been designed with great attention to detail, ensuring maximum comfort and functionality.

A 4% DLD (Dubai Land Department) fee applies to all real estate transactions in Dubai and must be paid in addition to the property's purchase price.

Keymaven’s commitment to redefining the real estate landscape is evident in every project, where meticulous attention to detail and innovative design converge to create spaces that are both functional and aesthetically pleasing. By focusing on sustainable practices and cutting-edge technology, Keymaven ensures that each development not only meets the highest standards of luxury but also caters to the evolving needs of modern residents.

The company’s philosophy is to envision, design, construct, deliver, and oversee real estate ventures that prioritize the growth and potential of each individual. By creating high-end yet valuable properties, Keymaven ensures that every detail contributes to the comfort, well-being, and personal development of its residents.
